  <compounddef id="group__dataloader__module" kind="group">
    <compoundname>dataloader_module</compoundname>
    <title>DataLoader Module</title>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Efficient data loading and batching for training. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<sect1 id="group__dataloader__module_1dataloader_overview">
<title>Overview</title>
<para>The DataLoader module provides functionality for efficient data loading, batching, and shuffling during model training and evaluation.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="group__dataloader__module_1dataloader_features_mod">
<title>Features</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Batch construction from graph data</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Shuffling and randomization</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Multi-threaded loading</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>K-fold cross-validation support</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Device placement (CPU/CUDA)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="group__dataloader__module_1dataloader_batching_mod">
<title>Batching</title>
<para>The dataloader creates batches by:<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>Collecting multiple graphs</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Concatenating node features with batch indexing</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Adjusting edge indices for the batched graph</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Stacking graph-level features</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classdataloader" kindref="compound">dataloader</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
</sect1>
    </detaileddescription>
